{"word":"G186 - ἀκλινής - aklinḗs - ak-lee-nace' - Without wavering","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἀκλινής</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">aklinḗs</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ak-lee-nace'</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Without wavering</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"அசைவில்லாத - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"not inclining, firm, unmoved"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G1 - Α - A - al'-fah/1\">G1</a> (as a negative particle) and <a href=\"#/G2827 - κλίνω - klínō - klee'-no/2827\">G2827</a>; <i>not leaning</i>, (that is, (figuratively) <i>firm:</i> - without wavering.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}